# jUnit Report

The jUnit Report binary is able to parse OpenShift Origin `test-cmd` test output and convert it into jUnit XML. This package is based on work by Joel Stemmer at [`go-junit-report`](https://github.com/jstemmer/go-junit-report).

## Installation

The `junitreport` binary can be built with:

```sh
$ hack/build-go.sh cmd/junitreport
````

## Usage

`junitreport` expects the input file to be given directly:

```sh
$ JUNIT_OUTPUT=1 hack/test-cmd.sh | junitreporter > report.xml
```

or passed in as an argument:

```sh
$ JUNIT_OUTPUT=1 hack/test-cmd.sh > /tmp/artifact.txt
$ junitreporter -f /tmp/artifact.txt > report.xml
```